response.original_title: Agent Tony Spears- The Return of Agent Tony Spears!!!
response.overview: Agent Tony Spears has been in retirement for a few years enjoying his retirement at his huge ranch in Eldoret, Uasin Gishu County in Kenya. He has been recalled to assist the Kenyan authorities in Haiti. Agent Spears has asked the Kenyan authorities to stay back in Kenya while he goes to Haiti to complete the mission!!
